800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ubisoft-five-former-executives-arrested-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ubisoft-five-former-executives-arrested-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/ubisoft-five-former-executives-arrested-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>在对育碧办公室内涉嫌性侵犯和骚扰的事件进行调查后，五名前<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/ubisoft">育碧</a>高管被捕。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/if-you-care-about-video-games-care-about-the-people-who-make-them-too-2699898">如果您关心视频游戏，也关心制作它们的人</a></strong></li></ul><p>据<a href="https://www.liberation.fr/culture/jeux-video/affaire-ubisoft-cinq-gardes-a-vue-dans-le-cadre-dune-enquete-pour-agressions-et-harcelements-sexuels-20231004_HS6Z3IPLHNGKZEPBZEM3W5WHRU/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《解放报》报道</em></a>，三人于 10 月 3 日被捕，另外两人于 10 月 4 日被拘留。其中包括汤米·弗朗索瓦 (Tommy François) 和塞尔日·哈斯科埃 (Serge Hascoët)，他们在指控公开后都离开了出版商。</p><p>弗朗索瓦是育碧巴黎分公司负责编辑和创意服务的副总裁，负责<em>制作<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/assassins-creed">《刺客信条》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/prince-of-persia">《波斯王子》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/tom-clancys-the-division-2">《汤姆克兰西：全境封锁》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/watch-dogs">《看门狗》</a></em>等系列作品。 </p><figure id="attachment_3269396" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3269396" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3269396" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/assassins-creed-future.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/assassins-creed-future.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/assassins-creed-future-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/assassins-creed-future-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/assassins-creed-future-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/assassins-creed-future-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/assassins-creed-future-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3269396" class="wp-caption-text"> 《刺客信条》宇宙。信用：育碧。</figcaption></figure><p>哈斯科特于 1988 年加入育碧，担任首席创意官，负责监督<em>《刺客信条》</em>以及《汤姆克兰西》的两部作品<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/rainbow-six"><em>《彩虹六号》</em></a>和<em>《幽灵行动》</em>的重启和复兴。</p><p>几年前， <a href="http://www.dulcamarra.net/2020/07/02/english-translation-of-a-press-article-by-liberation-about-allegations-against-ubisot-about-sexual-misconduct/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《Libération》</em>在 2020 年发布的报告</a>中指责育碧“在业内第三大工作室内部存在有毒系统，由贱民主导，受到‘人力资源之墙’的保护”。</p><p>作为回应，育碧<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/ubisoft-pledges-company-wide-overhaul-after-sexual-misconduct-allegations-2698230">开始对这些说法进行调查</a>，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/ubisoft-ceo-outlines-changes-to-company-following-misconduct-investigation-2770712">进行了内部调查</a>，得出的结论是五分之一的员工感觉“在工作环境中没有得到充分的尊重或安全”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3502565" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3502565" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3502565" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/tom-clancys-the-division-3-announced-ubisoft-julian-gerighty.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/tom-clancys-the-division-3-announced-ubisoft-julian-gerighty.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/tom-clancys-the-division-3-announced-ubisoft-julian-gerighty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/tom-clancys-the-division-3-announced-ubisoft-julian-gerighty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/tom-clancys-the-division-3-announced-ubisoft-julian-gerighty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content